本模板提供管線排序和最多至16個分類，這些分類將根據給出第一個引數（參數）名稱或字符串作為排序。由此產生出一系列<nowiki>[[Category:{{{2}}}|{{{1}}}]] [[Category:{{{3}}}|{{{1}}}]]</nowiki>... <nowiki>[[Category:{{{16}}}|{{{1}}}]]</nowiki>宣告，其必須為有效的模板或分類空間。

*Duplication of another page's category requires merely navigation to the page, swiping the category strings off the page category lists, and returning to paste them into this template. 

*The swiped category names will already be separated by pipe characters, leaving little to do, save close the curly braces, and choose a first perameter (normally the {{Mta|Help:magic word}}: <nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}</nowiki> is best&mdash;be careful not to enclose any leading spaces!)

* If only one argument is given, the template treats that as a category name, and automatically pipetricks the inclusion to  <nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}</nowiki>. 
